    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained example of a true driver\u2019s car. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a cherished weekend cruiser and a reliable daily companion. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful road use. Step inside to a smoke-free cabin where the leather remains supple and the dashboard is free of cracks or sun damage; only the driver\u2019s side bolster shows the slightest hint of entry wear. All electronic components, from the premium audio system to the dual-zone climate control, function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine pulls strongly and smoothly, benefiting from a documented history of synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. The transmission shifts with precision, and the suspension remains taut, providing a confident feel through every corner. Recently fitted with a fresh set of performance tires and high-quality brake pads, this car is turn-key and ready for its next chapter. I have all service records available for review and invite any serious buyer to experience the quality in person.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
