    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 Honda S2000 (AP2) is a precision-engineered example of the legendary roadster. At its heart is the F22C1 2.2L DOHC VTEC inline-four, offering a broader torque curve and an 8,000 RPM redline. The longitudinal powertrain is mated to a 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring tactile engagement and superior corner-exit traction. The high-X-bone monocoque chassis provides exceptional torsional rigidity, complemented by a factory-tuned double-wishbone suspension at all four corners. Recent mechanical maintenance includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and a full flush of the hydraulic systems. This vehicle remains mechanically sound with crisp gear synchronization and linear throttle response, perfect for the purist seeking a communicative driving experience.",
